Multi-emissive CDs were synthetized using 100 mg of A. platensis dispersed in 15 mL of the corresponding solvent by one-step process at 180 °C for 2–5 h (Fig. 1
                        ). The obtained suspensions were sonicated (4 h), centrifuged at 13000 rpm (30 min) and filtered. Table 1
                         shows the nomenclature corresponding to each sample.
